    FormSecurityHanlder, SpnegoSecurityHandler

    public abstract class DrillHttpConstraintSecurityHandler
extends org.eclipse.jetty.security.ConstraintSecurityHandler
    Accessor class that extends the ConstraintSecurityHandler to expose protected method's for start and stop of Handler. This is needed since now DrillHttpSecurityHandlerProvider composes of 2 security handlers - For FORM and SPNEGO and has responsibility to start/stop of those handlers.
